## DEPLOYMENT PIPELINE

```
Marketing site:  bash scripts/deploy-marketing.sh {stage}
API backend:     source scripts/env-api-dev.sh && bash scripts/deploy.sh {stage}
Web (ECS):       bash scripts/deploy-web-ecs.sh {stage}
Web env vars:    bash scripts/print-stack-outputs-for-web.sh {stage}
Size preflight:  bash scripts/infra-template-size-check.sh
```

Stack deploy order (automatic via CloudFormation dependencies):
1. DataLayerStack (DynamoDB, S3, Secrets)
2. AppSamStackV2 (primary Lambdas — incidents, CAD, QA, campus, venue, stream)
3. AppSam2Stack (language, analytics, retention, comms)
4. AppSam3Stack (video/media, agency admin, RC admin/desktop)
5. AppSam4Stack (billing/payments, Ring Connect)
6. AppSamQrStack (QR location management)

---

## TESTING

- Unit tests: Vitest
- Role/auth tests: always test that wrong roles get 403, not just that correct roles get 200
- Dashboard section tests: verify each role sees ONLY its intended widgets
- Route routing tests: verify product vertical roles do NOT reach PSAP jurisdiction routes
- Run: `npm run test` from monorepo root

